to hear from you about this topic- do you
think the world will ever be vegan? Will the

00:03:55.230 --> 00:04:00.099
animals ever achieve the freedom they so richly
deserve? Do you think this can happen in our

00:04:00.099 --> 00:04:05.409
lifetime? Do you struggle with feeling overwhelmed
by all the suffering out there? Let me know

00:04:05.409 --> 00:04:10.650
